WEBVTT

00:00:00.733 --> 00:00:02.027
dertseyln zi vayter.

00:00:03.011 --> 00:00:09.030
vi gezogt, zaynen mir gekumen shoyn dem tsveytn mol in STUTTHOF. STUTTHOF yetst hot shoyn oysgezen in gantsn andersh

00:00:09.103 --> 00:00:10.768
vi dem ershtn mol.

00:00:11.094 --> 00:00:12.928
mir zaynen shoyn geshtanen

00:00:13.355 --> 00:00:15.965
gleyb ikh eynike monat for dem

00:00:16.123 --> 00:00:18.176
vi der krig hot zikh geendikt.

00:00:19.025 --> 00:00:23.810
un dan iz dortn keyn ordenung nisht gevezn. zey hobn gezukht alts tsu farnikhtn,

00:00:23.810 --> 00:00:27.764
alts tsu farshteln, alts tsu f- farshlepn.

00:00:27.783 --> 00:00:33.796
zey hobn geshosn dortn alemen oyf rekhts un oyf links. ikh gedenk a bild vi ikh bin gekumen dem tsveytn mol in STUTTHOF,

00:00:33.796 --> 00:00:39.067
dortn zaynen gelegn aroyfgeshtaplt eyner oyfn tsveytn toyte berg.

00:00:39.326 --> 00:00:41.834
fulkum zin fun vort berg.

00:00:42.262 --> 00:00:48.360
ikh gedenk vi yetst ze ikh vi zey hobn geshlept &lt;kedey&gt; vi makht men di berg? me darf dokh tsuzamenklaybn di toyte mentshn fun arum un arum,

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:50.039
tsukumen tsu dem ort un berg.

00:00:50.039 --> 00:00:54.696
iz zey hobn geshlept far a langn tsop a froy, shoyn a toyte natirlekh

00:00:54.696 --> 00:00:56.240
kedey tsutsukumen tsu dem,

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:57.343
tsu dem ort.

00:00:58.007 --> 00:01:00.752
un mir zaynen gevezn in a barak,

00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:02.290
di yidn.

00:01:02.310 --> 00:01:04.599
s'zaynen gevezn nokh andere barakes oykh fun polyakn.

00:01:04.773 --> 00:01:06.421
un in draytsn

00:01:06.798 --> 00:01:07.653
barak

00:01:08.891 --> 00:01:09.577
in

00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:12.297
STUTTHOF

00:01:12.297 --> 00:01:13.020
un

00:01:13.380 --> 00:01:15.377
do &lt;ho- -z&gt; oysgebrokhn

00:01:15.377 --> 00:01:17.359
mir derneentern zikh shoyn tsu

00:01:17.362 --> 00:01:18.825
kimat april.

00:01:19.522 --> 00:01:20.664
finef un fer-

00:01:19.573 --> 00:01:21.002
finf un fertsik.

00:01:21.311 --> 00:01:23.432
un do iz oysgebrokhn

00:01:24.230 --> 00:01:27.481
ti- a mageyfe tifus. tifus, tifus.

00:01:28.466 --> 00:01:29.304
ikh

00:01:29.799 --> 00:01:30.890
tsu a glik

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:31.863
a glik...

00:01:31.863 --> 00:01:32.640
ikh

00:01:32.668 --> 00:01:34.012
un nokh eyner,

00:01:34.220 --> 00:01:37.134
er heyst SAMUEL WERNER, a daytsher yid

00:01:37.595 --> 00:01:41.912
vos iz geven &lt;oykh&gt; fun Rige, fun Rige gekumen mit undz tsuzamen gevezn, er iz yetst in Oystralye.

00:01:41.949 --> 00:01:45.144
zaynen gevorn gekumen gev-, krank gevorn in tifus

00:01:45.144 --> 00:01:46.196
di ershte.

00:01:47.838 --> 00:01:54.121
hobn zey undz oyb me ken dos onrufn shpitol, nit shpitol, dos ken nit UNK zey hobn es ongerufn KRANKENRIVIER oyf

00:01:54.121 --> 00:01:55.008
oyf daytsh,

00:01:55.008 --> 00:01:59.016
ober a shpitol, nit shpitol, mit koykes, mit dray etazh,

00:01:59.016 --> 00:02:01.282
hobn zey undz avekgeshikt ahin

00:02:01.524 --> 00:02:03.408
un dortn hobn zey oykh geshikt

00:02:03.735 --> 00:02:08.134
polyakn, vi ikh hob gezogt dortn geven oykh polyakn un andere vos zaynen gevorn krank mit tifus,

00:02:09.033 --> 00:02:10.313
hobn zey oykh dortn geshikt.

00:02:10.313 --> 00:02:14.495
keyn refues, keyn zakh nit hobn zey dortn nit gegebn, gornisht nit.

00:02:14.940 --> 00:02:22.570
un fa- un, un yedn tog hobn ongehoybn fun dem yi- fun di yidishn blok tsendliker, tsendlik hobn zey geefnt a blok, a, a

00:02:22.570 --> 00:02:24.160
a r- a leydikn blok

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:25.163
un hobn dortn

00:02:25.166 --> 00:02:26.544
gevorfn di ale

00:02:26.988 --> 00:02:28.299
tifus-kranke.

00:02:29.132 --> 00:02:30.639
agev, ven ikh hob,

00:02:30.639 --> 00:02:35.086
vi ikh bin aroys fun dortn, hob ikh gezen durkhn fentster vi zey zaynen ale opgetrotn fun STUTTHOF,

00:02:35.086 --> 00:02:35.994
vi zey hobn

00:02:36.557 --> 00:02:39.741
untergetsundn dem blok mit di gantse

00:02:39.864 --> 00:02:40.854
mentshn.

00:02:41.417 --> 00:02:42.205
ikh hob

00:02:42.294 --> 00:02:47.278
gehat may- mayn ort, vu ikh bin gelegn krankerheyt, iz gevezn oyfn dritn etazh.

00:02:47.278 --> 00:02:51.873
tsum glik, s'iz gevezn shoyn dan gants kalt iz gevezn, kh'hob gehat eyn un fertsik grad zikher

00:02:52.115 --> 00:02:53.386
iz gevezn

00:02:53.386 --> 00:02:59.906
ofn, a lyuk, a bisl oybn epes vos un ikh hob gehat dortn luft, ober tsu geyn in tualet, oyb me ken dos onrufn tualet

00:02:59.979 --> 00:03:02.403
hob ikh gedarft arunter fun eyn

00:03:02.578 --> 00:03:04.361
mit eyn un fertsik grad

00:03:04.637 --> 00:03:05.530
un mit

00:03:05.530 --> 00:03:09.612
SHILSHUL, dos iz di ergste krankeyt, in a tifus

00:03:09.648 --> 00:03:10.908
geyn ahin.

00:03:12.416 --> 00:03:15.200
ikh gedenk az ikh bin gekumen in dem SOG-

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:16.041
-gerufenem

00:03:16.044 --> 00:03:18.165
KRANKENRIVIER, hob ikh gehat bay zikh

00:03:18.373 --> 00:03:19.262
dray

00:03:19.706 --> 00:03:20.696
papirosn.

00:03:22.203 --> 00:03:24.459
kh'hob tseteylt yedn papiros oyf helft.

00:03:24.684 --> 00:03:26.146
kh'hob gegebn dortn

00:03:26.456 --> 00:03:29.117
di vos zaynen geven mer gezunt, far yedn halbn

00:03:29.510 --> 00:03:32.458
papiros hot er mir gegebn a fleshele mit

00:03:33.054 --> 00:03:35.124
gekokhte vaser. far vos?

00:03:35.180 --> 00:03:41.671
vayle az nit keyn gekokhte oder andere zakhn krigt men a SHILSHUL un dan shtarbt men. fun SHILSHULn ken gornisht nit helfn.

00:03:42.588 --> 00:03:44.287
mir zaynen dortn

00:03:55.596 --> 00:03:57.297
ikh gleyb az a bisl

00:03:57.742 --> 00:03:59.694
iz do nit genoy

00:03:59.852 --> 00:04:00.572
ober

00:04:00.898 --> 00:04:04.166
ikh gleyb azoy fun STUTTHOF hobn zey undz avekgefirt oyfn

00:04:05.370 --> 00:04:06.276
oyfn

00:04:08.238 --> 00:04:10.716
linye vos iz gevezn MAMASH der front

00:04:10.716 --> 00:04:14.831
kedey avektsuleygn undz tsvishn di rusn un tsvishn di daytshn

00:04:16.203 --> 00:04:18.813
als, zey hobn gemeynt az efsher

00:04:18.988 --> 00:04:23.702
veln di rusn, zey veln zen, zey veln zen, dortn iz hunderter flikhtlingen hunder&lt;ter&gt;

00:04:23.702 --> 00:04:26.098
az zey veln zen, veln zey nit shisn

00:04:26.098 --> 00:04:29.152
un zey veln dan, iz shoyn hinter undz, hinter undz zaynen barakn

00:04:29.152 --> 00:04:31.368
hobn zey avekgeshtelt zeyer artilerye

00:04:33.247 --> 00:04:34.304
un

00:04:35.103 --> 00:04:39.260
natirlekh, mir hobn klor gezen az di rusn bamien zikh tsu shisn

00:04:39.260 --> 00:04:41.117
ariber undzere barakn.

00:04:41.162 --> 00:04:45.831
ober eyn mol hobn zey nat- nit getrofn. mentshn zaynen dortn gefaln.

00:04:47.253 --> 00:04:49.509
un dos iz

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:55.635
gevezn vos ikh hob aroysgenumen a &lt;fal&gt; tsvishn di frontn vos zey hobn undz avekgeleygt als als

00:04:55.691 --> 00:04:58.605
als tsu shitsn zeyere, zeyere soldatn.

00:04:58.863 --> 00:05:00.902
ober ikh muz zogn

00:05:00.922 --> 00:05:04.393
az der ort gleyb ikh fun vanet mir zaynen gekumen hot geheysn...

00:05:06.896 --> 00:05:08.021
neyn. ikh gedenk nisht.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:12.436
ikh reyd yetst vayter vegn dem ort vu ikh bin gevezn krank, in tifus.

00:05:12.436 --> 00:05:14.265
mir zaynen gelegn ale tifus-kranke.

00:05:14.388 --> 00:05:15.901
tsvey yidn, di iberike ale.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:21.397
di rusn, vi gezogt, hobn zikh genumen derneentern, un mir hobn genumen shoyn hern di artilerye-shosn fun di rusn

00:05:21.397 --> 00:05:23.677
un me darf antloyfn, di daytshn darfn antloyfn.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.987
z- zey, zaynen geven arumgeringlt nit nor oyf der yaboshe

00:05:27.987 --> 00:05:29.556
nor oykh arum yam.

00:05:29.559 --> 00:05:34.076
zey hobn gehat a tsutrit tsum yam, epes a eynike finf kilometer, ober nit keyn

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:38.683
port, ober a, a breg, a geveynlekher breg fun yam.

00:05:38.908 --> 00:05:42.345
ikh gedenk vi haynt, ikh bin gelegn oybn. ikh hob gekukt un ikh hob getrakht,

00:05:42.587 --> 00:05:45.433
vos vet zayn vet zayn. zoln zey undz lozn.

00:05:45.945 --> 00:05:47.503
vos vet zayn vet zayn.

00:05:47.503 --> 00:05:49.739
zaynen gekumen oykh hoykhe ofitsern

00:05:49.775 --> 00:05:52.756
un ikh her, ikh farshtey a bisl daytsh, ikh her vi zey zogn "JA.

00:05:52.965 --> 00:05:54.000
WIR LASSEN SIE."

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.136
"mir lozn zey."

00:05:56.913 --> 00:06:01.548
faln, a, a b- a bombe vet faln, &lt;oybe vet&gt; nit faln efsher veln kumen di rusn, efsher &lt;vet fort zayn&gt;.

00:06:02.668 --> 00:06:03.641
di mentshn,

00:06:04.136 --> 00:06:07.573
in a dray fir sho arum zaynen gekumen vider hoykhe ofitsern

00:06:08.490 --> 00:06:09.668
un zey zogn

00:06:09.688 --> 00:06:10.830
zey nemen zey mit.

00:06:10.886 --> 00:06:11.893
mir nemen zey mit.

00:06:12.675 --> 00:06:14.526
vos heyst? hobn zey nokh tsugeleygt,

00:06:14.649 --> 00:06:16.314
der vos ken nit geyn

00:06:16.522 --> 00:06:19.081
f- di finf kilometer tsum breg yam

00:06:19.155 --> 00:06:20.364
veln mir zey gebn

00:06:20.927 --> 00:06:22.932
last-vogns, mir'n zey avekfirn

00:06:22.968 --> 00:06:24.414
un di vos kenen geyn

00:06:24.538 --> 00:06:25.511
zoln geyn.

00:06:26.006 --> 00:06:28.307
mir hobn shoyn gehat hinter zikh fir yor

00:06:28.307 --> 00:06:29.679
NISAYON

00:06:30.123 --> 00:06:36.311
fun zeyere toyves vos zey tuen, mir hobn kimat geven zikher di vos kenen nit geyn veln zey take nemen oyf mashines ober tsum shisn.

00:06:36.941 --> 00:06:44.591
un ikh hob batrakht, vi s'vet zayn vet zayn. mit eyn un fertsik grad vi s'vet zayn vet zayn. ikh &lt;vel ken-&gt;, ikh gedenk, kh'hob aroyfgevorfn, ikh hob gehat aza dekele dortn gelegn im

00:06:44.636 --> 00:06:46.959
oyf zikh, un mir zaynen gegangen

00:06:47.100 --> 00:06:50.621
di fir kilometer. mir zaynen gegangen un gegangen

00:06:50.778 --> 00:06:54.755
oyf mentshn men- oyfn veg di fir kilometer. mentshn zaynen gefaln, hobn zey zey geshosn

00:06:54.879 --> 00:06:56.291
un mir zaynen dergangen.

00:06:56.651 --> 00:06:58.110
vos hobn mir gezen far zikh?

00:06:58.110 --> 00:07:00.023
az f- vayt fun breg

00:07:00.060 --> 00:07:02.192
a hundert, hundert fuftsik meter

00:07:02.237 --> 00:07:05.069
vayle vi gezogt, s'iz nit geven keyn port ze- di

00:07:05.069 --> 00:07:07.412
di shif hot nit gekent tsuforn tsum breg

00:07:07.923 --> 00:07:12.595
zaynen geshtanen tsvey dray barzhes. barzhe, a barzhe, dos iz

00:07:12.595 --> 00:07:14.685
a groyse last-

00:07:16.968 --> 00:07:17.840
shif

00:07:17.998 --> 00:07:19.190
on a motor

00:07:19.500 --> 00:07:21.261
vos hot oybn an efenung,

00:07:21.261 --> 00:07:25.142
durkh im flegt men in normale tsaytn onladn skhoyre

00:07:25.187 --> 00:07:28.455
un di tsvey dray barzhes flegt shik- shlepn

00:07:28.511 --> 00:07:30.615
a shif mit a motor.

00:07:31.532 --> 00:07:38.016
hobn zey fun breg biz der barzhe nokh oybn, di barzhe shteyt ammeynstns tsvey a halb biz dray meter nokh oybn

00:07:38.016 --> 00:07:39.743
fun OBERflakh fun vaser.

00:07:39.743 --> 00:07:43.170
hobn zey oyfgemakht a lange, lange bret

00:07:43.327 --> 00:07:44.705
a shmole

00:07:45.285 --> 00:07:46.275
on a

00:07:47.597 --> 00:07:48.784
MAAKE

00:07:48.784 --> 00:07:52.184
on a onshpar fun beyde zaytn.

00:07:52.220 --> 00:07:55.576
di mentshn vos zaynen gekumen zaynen geven tifus-kranke

00:07:55.576 --> 00:07:56.765
mit

00:07:56.810 --> 00:08:01.180
hoykhe temperatur, un m'hot gezogt "geyt! geyt &lt;nor&gt;."

00:08:01.180 --> 00:08:03.591
oybn iz geshtanen eyner a daytsh.

00:08:03.591 --> 00:08:05.701
ver s'hot derlebt tsutsugeyn biz oybn

00:08:05.701 --> 00:08:07.757
hot er a shtup geton

00:08:07.982 --> 00:08:09.270
vayle key- fun

00:08:09.270 --> 00:08:11.447
untn, fun oybn biz untn

00:08:11.447 --> 00:08:14.493
fun der barzhe iz nit gevezn keyn

00:08:14.493 --> 00:08:17.252
keyn trep aruntertsugeyn di tsvey, tsvey a halb meter.

00:08:17.252 --> 00:08:19.383
derlangen a shtup, faln untn.

00:08:19.541 --> 00:08:21.513
oyfn veg vi gezogt, mentshn flegn faln

00:08:21.513 --> 00:08:24.069
un di mentshn hobn mir gezen vos me hot gebrakht fun

00:08:24.069 --> 00:08:26.761
vos hobn nit gekent geyn hot men alemen geshosn

00:08:26.797 --> 00:08:27.942
un azoy

00:08:27.942 --> 00:08:30.200
hobn zey ongeladn in a barzhe

00:08:32.130 --> 00:08:34.279
hunderter mentshn

00:08:34.279 --> 00:08:35.662
one vaser

00:08:35.662 --> 00:08:38.114
one sh- one gornisht.

00:08:38.676 --> 00:08:42.653
nor vedlik aykh zogn, mayn shprakh iz mir

00:08:42.727 --> 00:08:46.352
orem tsu dertseyln. ikh hob azoy fil durkhgemakht far di yorn

00:08:46.355 --> 00:08:49.994
ober di nekht vos zaynen dortn hot zikh opgeshpilt

00:08:50.304 --> 00:08:53.153
iz veys ikh epes vos vel ikh dertseyln.

00:08:53.153 --> 00:08:54.753
geshreyen,

00:08:55.637 --> 00:08:57.859
mentshn vos zaynen oysgegangen,

00:08:58.235 --> 00:09:01.059
geshreyen fun di shtarkere.

00:09:01.059 --> 00:09:05.202
s'iz nit gevezn az m'iz gezesn, nit geven keyn luft. m'iz gezesn, gelegn eyner oyfn tsveytn.

00:09:05.202 --> 00:09:08.366
der shtarkerer flegt zikh bamien aroyftsukrikhn

00:09:08.366 --> 00:09:09.590
oyfn shvakhern

00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:10.982
kedey er zol hobn luft.

00:09:10.982 --> 00:09:15.648
di mentshn hobn zikh bamit tsu krikhn tsum lyuk oybn vos iz gevezn ofn

00:09:15.648 --> 00:09:17.166
vu s'iz gevezn a bisl luft.

00:09:17.166 --> 00:09:18.733
di mentshn hobn

00:09:18.924 --> 00:09:22.836
gezukht baym tsveytn a shtikl broyt, a shtikl vaser, epes vos.

00:09:22.836 --> 00:09:24.336
dos iz gevezn

00:09:24.847 --> 00:09:25.854
a gan-

00:09:26.788 --> 00:09:27.992
gehenem

00:09:28.020 --> 00:09:29.482
SHEL MATA.

00:09:32.171 --> 00:09:33.684
yedn inderfri

00:09:33.926 --> 00:09:36.064
flegt durkhgeyn an S.S.nik

00:09:36.322 --> 00:09:38.814
arunterlozn a sh- shtrik

00:09:39.123 --> 00:09:41.530
fun oybn, fun lyuk nokh untn,

00:09:41.823 --> 00:09:43.370
heysn tsuzamen

00:09:43.950 --> 00:09:45.733
arumnemen arum boykh.

00:09:46.059 --> 00:09:49.912
di vos zaynen shoyn ye geshtorbn &lt;oder&gt; vos zaynen nokh nit geshtorbn

00:09:49.957 --> 00:09:52.713
flegt er zey aroyfnemen nokh oybn aroyftsien

00:09:52.713 --> 00:09:54.814
mit a meser tsu shnaydn di boykh

00:09:54.814 --> 00:09:57.056
dermit er zol n- zoln

00:09:57.163 --> 00:09:59.826
ah, der, der vaser

00:10:00.386 --> 00:10:03.134
a mentsh vos iz nit opgeshnitn di boykh

00:10:03.134 --> 00:10:06.011
der vaser varft im aroys in nokh a gevise tsol teg.

00:10:06.011 --> 00:10:07.045
in aza fal

00:10:07.473 --> 00:10:13.694
un azoy zaynen mir arumgeshvumen bizn akhtn may finf un fertsik

00:10:14.038 --> 00:10:16.682
ven di krig hot zikh geendikt.

00:10:16.772 --> 00:10:19.433
mir zaynen geblibn oyf di barzhes

00:10:19.826 --> 00:10:21.559
tsvey oder dray teg

00:10:21.868 --> 00:10:25.375
un der hoypt MENAHEL

00:10:25.375 --> 00:10:29.517
fun Roytn Kreyts fun Shvedn vos er hot geheysn FOLKE BERNADOTTE

00:10:29.517 --> 00:10:30.961
hot geshikt dan

00:10:30.961 --> 00:10:35.630
a groyse shif, a pasazhir-shif, m'hot gekent shoyn vi a mentsh UNK.

00:10:35.630 --> 00:10:37.407
mir zaynen koym-koym ariber ahin

00:10:37.427 --> 00:10:41.651
un men hot undz ale tifus-kranke aribergefirt in Shvedn

00:10:41.696 --> 00:10:45.133
tsu heyln undz, ver s'iz geshtorbn, ver s'hot gelebt.

00:10:46.607 --> 00:10:47.394
yetst.

00:10:47.906 --> 00:10:49.706
mir zaynen gekumen in Shvedn.

00:10:50.707 --> 00:10:57.519
hot men undz zeyer fayn bahandlt, zeyer fayn, m'hot zikh, me zogt m'hot undz m'hot zikh mit undz getsatsket.

00:10:58.098 --> 00:10:59.206
in di

00:11:00.900 --> 00:11:03.392
krankn-hayzer vu mir zaynen gelegn

00:11:03.633 --> 00:11:08.043
flegt men nisht araynlozn, az s'iz gevezn a klepedike krankeyt, a onshtekndike krankeyt,

00:11:08.043 --> 00:11:12.031
nor di fentster zaynen gevezn ofn. s'iz shoyn gevezn, flegn zey kumen mit peklekh

00:11:12.122 --> 00:11:13.180
un varfn

00:11:15.294 --> 00:11:16.666
durkh di fentster

00:11:16.666 --> 00:11:18.410
far undz farshidene zakhn.

00:11:19.142 --> 00:11:20.908
me hot undz

00:11:21.048 --> 00:11:24.434
nokh dem vi m'iz, &lt;az mer&gt; oder veyniker gekent shteyn oyf di fis

00:11:25.115 --> 00:11:27.523
hot men far undz

00:11:28.035 --> 00:11:32.079
geratevete fun Baltikum, fun Lite, Letland un Estland

00:11:32.895 --> 00:11:35.255
hot di &lt;me-&gt; regirung oyf ir kheshbn

00:11:35.291 --> 00:11:36.720
FÜR RECHNUNG

00:11:36.776 --> 00:11:39.386
genumen a vile nit vayt fun

00:11:39.729 --> 00:11:43.244
Shtokholm vos hot geheysn der ort NEGLINGE lebn yam

00:11:43.244 --> 00:11:44.620
a vunderbar sheyner

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:46.164
ort, a datshner ort

00:11:46.164 --> 00:11:48.831
un dortn hobn zey undz gekormet un gegesn

00:11:48.831 --> 00:11:50.813
un mir hobn zikh dortn geheylt, un dortn

00:11:50.813 --> 00:11:55.900
hobn mir, flegn mir alts zayn tsuzamen &lt;mit di letishe&gt;

00:11:55.900 --> 00:11:57.572
&lt;in&gt; UNK Shtokholm zaynen gevezn

00:11:57.617 --> 00:11:59.774
fun a mol nokh, fun forn krig,

00:11:59.774 --> 00:12:02.043
yidn vos zaynen gekumen fun di baltishe lender

00:12:02.043 --> 00:12:04.254
un zey flegn yedn ovnt kumen tsu undz

00:12:04.254 --> 00:12:08.529
un brengen farshidene zakhn, mir UNK zoln hobn tsu esn un tsu trinken

00:12:08.889 --> 00:12:09.645
un

00:12:09.665 --> 00:12:14.801
ven mir hobn zikh genumen opkhapn a bisl un gezunter vern

00:12:14.801 --> 00:12:15.686
hobn mir

00:12:15.723 --> 00:12:16.952
ongefangen

00:12:16.952 --> 00:12:18.806
tsu zukhn arbet.

00:12:19.014 --> 00:12:22.755
ver es hot dervayle khasene gehat, ver dervayle hot gekrogn arbet

00:12:22.997 --> 00:12:25.945
un iz aroys fun, fun NEGLINGE.

00:12:27.030 --> 00:12:31.091
ikh hob bakumen arbet in a groyse hurt-firme

00:12:31.417 --> 00:12:33.453
fun pelts, bay a

00:12:33.594 --> 00:12:36.710
velkhe der balebos zaynen gevezn tsvey yidn, eyner fun

00:12:37.728 --> 00:12:39.477
Ungarn, eyner fun Letland

00:12:39.618 --> 00:12:41.789
vos zaynen gekumen natirlekh forn krig

00:12:42.335 --> 00:12:45.654
un ikh hob bay im, er hot mir genumen tsu zikh

00:12:45.744 --> 00:12:47.560
tsu der arbet.

00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:49.479
yetst vil ikh dertseyln a por verter

00:12:49.507 --> 00:12:51.572
az ikh hob zikh shoyn geratevet un ikh hob

00:12:51.617 --> 00:12:56.218
tsu zikh gekumen, hob ikh vider genumen trakhtn, vu iz mayn foter un mayn muter un di shvester?

00:12:59.227 --> 00:13:00.352
un ot

00:13:02.062 --> 00:13:03.204
hob ikh genumen,

00:13:03.767 --> 00:13:05.620
ikh hob avekgeshribn a kartl

00:13:05.640 --> 00:13:09.414
in der sh- gevezene shtot-farvaltung, fun mayn shtetele, fun Korsovke,

00:13:10.584 --> 00:13:13.042
ver ikh bin un vos ikh bin un vemen ikh zukh.

00:13:15.225 --> 00:13:17.570
ikh veys nit vi azoy di kart-

00:13:17.570 --> 00:13:18.487
di kartl

00:13:18.532 --> 00:13:20.771
iz gekumen ergets vu

00:13:21.519 --> 00:13:23.285
tsu mayne bakante

00:13:23.713 --> 00:13:26.436
vos zey hobn dos dertrogn tsu mayn muter

00:13:26.436 --> 00:13:27.943
un mayn shvester

00:13:28.252 --> 00:13:29.023
un

00:13:41.634 --> 00:13:42.573
oy!

00:13:48.165 --> 00:13:50.775
un in eyn sheynem tog hob ikh gekrogn

00:13:51.219 --> 00:13:52.260
a telegram

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:57.474
oyf-

00:13:58.290 --> 00:13:59.359
&lt;untershribn&gt;

00:13:59.370 --> 00:14:00.380
Rive

00:14:00.380 --> 00:14:01.204
mame.

00:14:04.230 --> 00:14:06.317
kh'hob farshtanen natirlekh az der foter iz geshtorbn.

00:14:10.693 --> 00:14:12.088
yetst

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:14.248
in zeks un fertsikstn yor

00:14:14.372 --> 00:14:15.936
hob ikh khasene gehat.

00:14:16.211 --> 00:14:19.715
ikh hob gearbet, vi gezogt, in aza f-, in a, in der firme.

00:14:20.177 --> 00:14:23.023
kh'hob gearbet dortn biz ende eyn un fuftsik.

00:14:23.231 --> 00:14:28.895
ikh hob dertseylt fun onfang az ikh hob gehat a shvester in Erets-Yisroel, in KVUTSAT GEVA.

00:14:29.323 --> 00:14:32.507
un ikh hob zikh mit ir natirlekh ibergeshribn.

00:14:34.470 --> 00:14:37.249
in Shvedn iz gevezn GAN EDEN SHEL MATA.

00:14:37.338 --> 00:14:45.292
arum un arum in gants Eyrope iz di industrye gevezn tseshmetert un tseklapt, un dos iz gevezn a industrye a lebedike alts. me hot gefodert fun ale zaytn

00:14:45.292 --> 00:14:48.201
arbeter, nem, gib nor arbet, arbet.

00:14:48.881 --> 00:14:53.060
un di materyele lage iz dan geven zeyer a gute in Shvedn

00:14:53.927 --> 00:14:56.784
ober ikh bin gevezn ful mayn harts mit

00:14:56.784 --> 00:15:00.401
tsienistishe zakhn vos ikh hob zikh gehodevet in shtub azoy

00:15:00.558 --> 00:15:03.289
un az in akht un fertsiktn yor iz nokh gevorn

00:15:03.292 --> 00:15:04.969
di yidishe medine

00:15:04.997 --> 00:15:09.294
bin ikh shoyn dortn kimat gezesn oyf shpilkes. natirlekh hob ikh gevust

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:15.740
az di lage in Erets-Yisroel iz zeyer a shvere. ershtns hot mir mayn shvester geshribn. tsveytns fun di tsaytung.

00:15:16.370 --> 00:15:19.194
un ikh hob bashlosn dokh trots dem

00:15:19.194 --> 00:15:21.326
az ikh bin gezesn in aza ganeydn

00:15:21.635 --> 00:15:23.418
a materyeln volt ikh gezogt

00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:26.644
visndik

00:15:26.647 --> 00:15:27.632
tsu forn

00:15:27.632 --> 00:15:29.088
in Erets-Yisroel.

00:15:30.140 --> 00:15:31.872
ikh gedenk az ikh fleg geyn

00:15:32.452 --> 00:15:36.344
erleydikn di papirn in di shvedishe anshtaltn,

00:15:36.671 --> 00:15:39.298
zey hobn oykh fun di tsaytung gevust vos do tut zikh.

00:15:39.438 --> 00:15:41.508
zey hobn gezogt "gut, fayn.

00:15:41.885 --> 00:15:43.972
vilst forn. ober vart nokh.

00:15:44.028 --> 00:15:47.870
dortn iz dokh azoy shver yetst. do iz dokh azoy gut, vart nokh.

00:15:47.870 --> 00:15:49.963
nokh a por yor, nokh a por yor."

00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:54.632
un nu, fun dest vegn bin ikh avekgeforn in eyn un fuftsiktn yor.

00:15:54.660 --> 00:15:59.329
natirlekh az do iz gevezn zeyer, zeyer shver fun onfang, un iber hoypt farglaykh

00:15:59.908 --> 00:16:02.808
in, mit Shvedn.

00:16:02.844 --> 00:16:06.149
ikh ken zikh dermonen, ikh bin gegangen tsu a dokter in eyn un fuftsiktn yor

00:16:06.185 --> 00:16:08.356
in KHADERA hobn mir gelebt

00:16:08.818 --> 00:16:14.145
un eyn un fuftsiktn yor iz geven naye OLIM, a groyse zakh, haynt iz dos andersh in gantsn.

00:16:14.657 --> 00:16:18.029
fregt mir der dokter "fun vanet zayt ir?" dokter &lt;MENATSE&gt; hot er geheysn.

00:16:18.029 --> 00:16:19.916
zog ikh "ikh bin gekumen fun Shvedn."

00:16:20.715 --> 00:16:23.426
gedenk ikh vi haynt, er hot getrakht un getrakht.

00:16:24.191 --> 00:16:26.188
"ZU HI KHALUTSIUT" zogt er mir.

00:16:26.188 --> 00:16:27.943
zog ikh "dokter, fun vanet veyst ir?"

00:16:27.943 --> 00:16:32.296
zogt er "ANI KARATI, ikh hob geleyent di letste tsaytn a sakh zeyer vegn Shvedn.

00:16:32.296 --> 00:16:35.440
ZUHI," zogt er, "KHALUTSIUT, az du kenst kumen," zogt er, "fun Shvedn."

00:16:36.476 --> 00:16:39.289
un, vi gezogt, bay undz iz geborn gevorn in Shvedn

00:16:40.020 --> 00:16:41.516
der elterer zun

00:16:42.804 --> 00:16:45.397
&lt;az ikh bin&gt; gekumen aher zaynen mir gevezn eyn un fuftsik

00:16:46.517 --> 00:16:48.199
iz er geven tsvey yor a halb

00:16:48.626 --> 00:16:51.644
in dray un fuftsiktn yor iz bay undz geborn gevorn der tsveyter zun

00:16:51.644 --> 00:16:53.042
ELIYAHU

00:16:53.351 --> 00:16:56.434
un in finf un fuftsiktn yor iz geborn gevorn undzer tokhter

00:16:56.557 --> 00:16:57.719
vos zi heyst

00:16:57.719 --> 00:16:58.526
Tsilye.

00:17:02.022 --> 00:17:04.789
ikh hob dokh gehat natirlekh, vi ale OLIM

00:17:04.789 --> 00:17:07.169
shverikeytn, gresere, klenere

00:17:07.169 --> 00:17:11.976
ober ikh hob zikh shtendik dermit getreyst az

00:17:12.403 --> 00:17:15.705
ikh bin do in an eygene land

00:17:20.013 --> 00:17:22.741
un dos hot mir a sakh, geholfn.

00:17:24.148 --> 00:17:32.158
azoy az natirlekh mit der tsayt, nokh ale shverikeytn, klenere, gresere, me hot zikh a bisl ayngeordnt &lt;do, mir hobn&gt; fertsn yor gelebt in KHADERA.

00:17:33.210 --> 00:17:37.105
dernokh zaynen mir ariber aher in RAMAT GAN.

00:17:37.142 --> 00:17:39.518
mayn froy hot oykh gearbet in &lt;SHEKEM&gt;

00:17:39.518 --> 00:17:41.473
geven a MENAHELET.

00:17:41.597 --> 00:17:43.515
un

00:17:44.094 --> 00:17:47.345
azoy lebn mir biz hayntikn tog, un nokh haynt

00:17:47.553 --> 00:17:50.484
viln mir hofn az mir hobn a gute, sheyne land.

00:17:51.232 --> 00:17:52.655
got zol gebn zol zayn

00:17:52.655 --> 00:17:53.623
sholem

00:17:55.198 --> 00:17:57.859
un di land zol

00:17:57.999 --> 00:18:00.190
t- PROTCVETAyenen

00:18:00.227 --> 00:18:02.297
 vi zogt men oyf yidish?

00:18:01.779 --> 00:18:02.600
bli&lt;m&gt;en.

00:18:02.420 --> 00:18:04.136
zol blu- bli&lt;m&gt;en.

00:18:05.576 --> 00:18:13.265
ikh hob aykh take gevolt fregn, bay vo- mit vos hot ir zikh basheftikt do in land, fun dem moment, ir zent geven fertsn yor in KHADERA, shpeter do in RAMAT GAN?

00:18:12.140 --> 00:18:14.120
ya. zayendik nokh in Shvedn,

00:18:14.148 --> 00:18:18.361
mayn froy hot gehat nokh fun Vilne, zey zaynen geforn a tsayt forn krig

00:18:18.603 --> 00:18:20.724
in ISRAEL in KHADERA kroyvim.

00:18:20.814 --> 00:18:25.182
zay hobn zikh farnumen mit, a mol &lt;ver hot es&gt; getrakht, iber hoypt vegn

00:18:25.182 --> 00:18:30.142
 miskher, az me fort in Erets-Yisroel, azoyne yidn vi mir, ful mit ZIONISMUS

00:18:29.302 --> 00:18:30.866
UNK

00:18:30.142 --> 00:18:32.952
UNK &lt;az ikh hob&gt; andersh in Shvedn nit getrakht

00:18:32.964 --> 00:18:34.337
ah, vos heyst, UNK

00:18:34.337 --> 00:18:37.583
&lt;mayn&gt; foter iz geven in groyse zakhn, in BUSINESS, in

00:18:38.043 --> 00:18:40.315
iz arayn zeen mir, veystu vos

00:18:40.423 --> 00:18:41.447
du breng

00:18:41.722 --> 00:18:44.622
bay aykh iz do a groyse firme a &lt;alveltlekhe&gt;, ATLAS DIESEL.

00:18:44.622 --> 00:18:45.955
breng a kompresor

00:18:45.955 --> 00:18:48.956
oyb ir veyst vos dos iz, vos hakt in shteyner,

00:18:49.552 --> 00:18:53.431
a kompresor. ATLAS DIESEL iz bay undz zeyer a groyse f- ongenumen

00:18:53.431 --> 00:18:57.034
un dos ken nit koyfn, &lt;zey hobn mir, mir hobn,&gt; di, di land hot gehat nit keyn dolarn

00:18:57.034 --> 00:19:00.043
vos me ken brengen fun oysland, mit hamers, mit ale mayses.

00:19:00.116 --> 00:19:04.093
ikh hob nit gevust iber hoypt vos iz a kompresor, vegn kompresor, vos kompresor,

00:19:04.672 --> 00:19:11.433
un mit groyse, groyse shverikeytn hobn mir tsuzamengeklibn gelt, un m'iz avek in ATLAS DIESEL, un mir hobn gekoyft dem gantsn

00:19:11.692 --> 00:19:12.851
TSIUD

00:19:15.793 --> 00:19:19.365
AUSSER-RUSTUNG AUF daytsh, dem gantsn TSIUD,

00:19:18.847 --> 00:19:19.635
yo.

00:19:19.758 --> 00:19:24.843
tsum kompresor, un dem kompresor, kh'hob nit gevust vi er zet oys afile, un mir zaynen gekumen aher

00:19:24.843 --> 00:19:26.655
mitn kompresor.

00:19:26.728 --> 00:19:33.003
nu, iz, HEYOT vi ikh hob dem gesheft nit gevust. me hot mir natirlekh oysgenutst, tsuzamen mitn kompresor,

00:19:33.003 --> 00:19:36.799
ober ikh hob gehat epes vos, fun onfang fun vos tsu lebn.

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:38.436
dernokh hob ikh gehat

00:19:38.473 --> 00:19:40.065
farkoyft dem kompresor

00:19:40.065 --> 00:19:41.994
un gekoyft a OTO MASA.

00:19:43.367 --> 00:19:47.583
a OTO MASA iz oykh gevezn, dortn zaynen gevezn shoyn alte VATIKIM

00:19:47.585 --> 00:19:51.033
vos hobn gehat zeyere,

00:19:51.033 --> 00:19:53.284
f- z- MISRADIM

00:19:53.542 --> 00:19:58.906
organizirte, un zey hobn gehat zeyere arbetn, iz geven zeyer shver arayntsukrikhn.

00:19:58.906 --> 00:20:02.811
fleg ikh shteyn azoy mitn OTO, flegt ver tsugeyn, fleg ikh vos tsu fardinen epes vos,

00:20:02.811 --> 00:20:05.656
biz SOF-SOF az mir hot zikh ayngegebn arayntsugeyn ergets vu

00:20:05.675 --> 00:20:07.239
in a MISRAD,

00:20:07.734 --> 00:20:12.169
ober dos iz nit gevezn mir PO DUSHE,

00:20:12.172 --> 00:20:15.103
vayle shofern fun

00:20:15.868 --> 00:20:18.512
mashines fun laykhte, es zaynen faran

00:20:18.753 --> 00:20:22.173
shofern nokhn kharakter un shofern

00:20:22.230 --> 00:20:25.464
nokhn MIKTSOA, nokhn

00:20:27.630 --> 00:20:29.126
nokhn fakh.

00:20:29.283 --> 00:20:30.881
ikh hob dos nit gekent

00:20:31.494 --> 00:20:32.394
alts

00:20:32.394 --> 00:20:35.741
baheybn, un ikh hob gezogt "ikh muz aroysgeyn fun dem MISRAD. dos iz nit far mir."

00:20:35.882 --> 00:20:37.237
un dan hob ikh

00:20:37.265 --> 00:20:38.998
gekrogn arbet

00:20:39.560 --> 00:20:40.680
in ELIT

00:20:40.680 --> 00:20:41.245
in

00:20:41.245 --> 00:20:43.149
RAMAT GAN in fabrik

00:20:43.492 --> 00:20:47.519
als SGAN MENAHEL KOAKH ADAM.

00:20:48.048 --> 00:20:49.139
far vos?

00:20:49.348 --> 00:20:50.945
der MENAHEL KOAKH ADAM

00:20:51.305 --> 00:20:57.917
iz gekum-, ELIT iz ge- aribergefirt zikh fun Rige. zi hot zikh ge- ah, ge- sh- gegrindet in Rige

00:20:57.937 --> 00:21:02.201
mit dem FRUMCHENKO mitn tatn

00:21:02.325 --> 00:21:03.973
un mitn MOSEVICSn

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:11.173
un dan hobn zey g- bay zikh gehaltn oykh a groysn ongeshteltn vos hot geheysn ELIYAHU GORDIN. ELIYAHU GORDIN iz gevezn mayn

00:21:11.201 --> 00:21:13.223
a korev a vayter, ober a korev.

00:21:13.223 --> 00:21:15.088
un fun zelbe shtetl un alts.

00:21:15.088 --> 00:21:16.708
az ikh bin gekumen aher

00:21:16.708 --> 00:21:20.831
iz er eyn mol tsu mir arayngeforn, er hot gevust mayn familye, mayn bildung, mayn alts.

00:21:21.292 --> 00:21:25.387
dos iz gevezn mistomen in etlekhe un, fir un zekhtsik oder finf un zekhtsik.

00:21:25.950 --> 00:21:32.137
fregt er mir, "Ayzik, du voltst veln arbetn in ELIT?" zog ikh "als vos?" zogt er "als mayn gehilf." un er hot mir dortn ayngeordnt,

00:21:32.835 --> 00:21:37.116
un dortn hob ikh gearbet, un dortn bin ikh aroys oyf pensye.

00:21:37.442 --> 00:21:43.461
un yetst shtelt zikh for tsu lebn vayter, AD MEA VESRIM zol got gebn!

00:21:43.230 --> 00:21:44.003
yo.

00:21:44.003 --> 00:21:45.463
azoy vi ir hot mir

00:21:45.272 --> 00:21:46.194
ye.

00:21:45.463 --> 00:21:50.413
zeyer gut dertseylt vos ir hot mir dertseylt, hob ikh aykh nokh gevolt fregn a frage.

00:21:51.212 --> 00:21:52.517
ir dertseylt az ir hot

00:21:52.528 --> 00:21:55.492
di kinder un eyniklekh, got tsu danken.

00:21:56.527 --> 00:22:02.529
kh'hob aykh gevolt fregn tsi mit der tsayt oyftsien di k- di kinder do, di merheyt in di land do

00:22:03.412 --> 00:22:05.907
hot ir ge- in

00:22:05.907 --> 00:22:11.017
farshidene faln zey dertseylt vos ir zent, vos ir hot adurkhgemakht in tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:22:10.955 --> 00:22:13.121
ikh muz zogn az ikh hob zey

00:22:13.149 --> 00:22:15.050
dertseylt veynik.

00:22:17.520 --> 00:22:18.454
poshet

00:22:18.465 --> 00:22:21.294
ikh hob nisht gezen az zey

00:22:21.907 --> 00:22:23.167
viln dos

00:22:23.392 --> 00:22:24.854
hern di ale

00:22:25.248 --> 00:22:28.468
geferlekhe momentn un shverikeytn

00:22:28.488 --> 00:22:31.000
vos der foter zeyerer hot durkhgemakht.

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:35.033
kh'hob eyn mol ongefangen tsu leyenen far mayne eyniklekh fun mayn tokhter

00:22:35.033 --> 00:22:36.881
vos lebn do in KHOLON

00:22:36.881 --> 00:22:38.827
dem bikhele mit dos,

00:22:39.086 --> 00:22:42.437
kh'hob gezen az zey zukhn tsu antloyfn fun dem.

00:22:42.528 --> 00:22:49.090
ikh veys, dos iz nit in gantsn in ordenung. efsher hobn zey ye gedarft, nit efsher nor zikher hobn zey gedarft

00:22:49.090 --> 00:22:51.905
visn vos zeyer foter iz durkhgegangen

00:22:53.126 --> 00:22:53.863
ober

00:22:54.088 --> 00:22:58.993
agev, di muter iz oykh durkhgegangen. di muter iz gevezn in BERGEN-BELSEN un in RAVENSBRÜCK un in

00:22:59.488 --> 00:23:00.613
ale fir yor,

00:23:01.057 --> 00:23:01.794
di muter.

00:23:02.964 --> 00:23:03.881
mir hobn

00:23:03.881 --> 00:23:05.878
nit matsliekh gevezn

00:23:06.474 --> 00:23:07.332
zey

00:23:07.332 --> 00:23:10.302
tsu dertseyln alts vos mir volt- hobn gevelt

00:23:10.305 --> 00:23:12.088
un voltn gevelt dertseyln,

00:23:12.397 --> 00:23:13.990
nit matsliekh gevezn.

00:23:14.557 --> 00:23:15.930
in algemeyn vos zey zogn

00:23:15.930 --> 00:23:16.900
az zey zaynen

00:23:16.900 --> 00:23:19.190
yidn, zey veysn fun ale MASORET

00:23:19.190 --> 00:23:20.849
&lt;zey veysn&gt; fun gants traditsye,

00:23:20.849 --> 00:23:23.478
zey zaynen efsher nit keyn frume, nit efsher, nit keyn frume

00:23:23.478 --> 00:23:26.619
ober zey veysn fun tsienizm un fun yidishkeyt. zey hobn do

00:23:26.639 --> 00:23:28.369
durkhgemakht der yingerer

00:23:28.369 --> 00:23:31.927
hot durkhgemakht di krig fun z- dray un zibetsik.

00:23:31.927 --> 00:23:35.479
der elterer hot durkhgemakht di krig fun zibn un zekhtsik un dray un zibetsik.

00:23:35.479 --> 00:23:38.837
zey zaynen ale, eyner iz a

00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:41.956
kapitan fun, fun a JUMBO.

00:23:42.148 --> 00:23:43.824
er hot geendikt do TEKHNION.

00:23:43.835 --> 00:23:46.276
un der tsveyter iz a

00:23:46.569 --> 00:23:49.652
inzhenir BAKHIR bay FORD in DETROIT.

00:23:49.927 --> 00:23:51.569
ober zaynen geblibn yidn.

00:23:51.569 --> 00:23:55.237
zey kumen aher shtendik. ot do, az zey kumen, zaynen zey vi bay zikh in der heym.

00:23:56.829 --> 00:23:59.642
ikh hob aykh gevolt nokh epes fregn.

00:24:00.103 --> 00:24:02.057
ir veyst vos iz a MESER?

00:24:02.043 --> 00:24:03.995
o ya, o ya.

00:24:02.057 --> 00:24:03.438
&lt;LIMSOR&gt; MESER.

00:24:04.372 --> 00:24:07.238
EZE MIN MESER HAITA OMER

00:24:05.672 --> 00:24:07.016
far vemen, vemen?

00:24:07.238 --> 00:24:10.664
LADOROT HABAIM, LAYELADIM SHELKHA, LANEKHADIM SHELKHA.

00:24:10.667 --> 00:24:12.838
KILEKAKH SHELKHA MEHASHOA?

00:24:13.029 --> 00:24:13.800
ya.

00:24:13.991 --> 00:24:16.213
MA HAITA OMER? BEKAMA MISHPATIM.

00:24:15.408 --> 00:24:17.427
ikh gedenk in Shvedn

00:24:17.501 --> 00:24:24.060
hob ikh zikh ibergeshribn mit maynem a khaver vos iz ahergeforn in zeks un draysik oder zibn in draysiktn yor.

00:24:24.133 --> 00:24:26.037
er iz a khaver fun KFAR BLUM

00:24:26.037 --> 00:24:28.329
vos iz dergangen do zeyer hoykh.

00:24:28.537 --> 00:24:30.129
der undzerer bavuster

00:24:30.129 --> 00:24:35.326
finants-minister, vi hot er geheysn, mit fertsik yor tsurik?

00:24:35.326 --> 00:24:36.348
nit Kaplan.

00:24:35.692 --> 00:24:36.766
ESHKOL?

00:24:36.348 --> 00:24:38.522
ney- finants-minister f-

00:24:37.785 --> 00:24:40.867
Kaplan iz geven eyner. der ershter iz geven Kaplan.

00:24:39.843 --> 00:24:42.453
vos hot getsoygn fun alemen di gelt geferlekh?

00:24:41.717 --> 00:24:43.129
 Sapir.

00:24:42.577 --> 00:24:45.460
Sapir! iz er gevezn mit im khaveyrim. kent ir zikh forshteln,

00:24:45.460 --> 00:24:46.723
er iz geven a hoykher mentsh

00:24:47.049 --> 00:24:48.090
un

00:24:52.820 --> 00:24:55.143
er hot mir geshribn, un ikh fleg im entfern

00:24:55.740 --> 00:24:59.762
oyf der frage vos ir fregt, gedenk ikh. dos iz gevezn bay mir di LEKAKH fun di

00:24:59.762 --> 00:25:01.421
fun di lagern, fun &lt;iber di yorn&gt;.

00:25:01.578 --> 00:25:04.357
dan iz nokh gevezn nokh eyder s'iz gevezn di medine.

00:25:05.055 --> 00:25:06.399
hob ikh im geshribn.

00:25:06.995 --> 00:25:07.985
nor

00:25:08.193 --> 00:25:10.157
farlozt zikh nit oyf keynem

00:25:10.202 --> 00:25:11.608
nor di gever

00:25:11.608 --> 00:25:13.689
lozt nisht aroys fun di hent.

00:25:15.011 --> 00:25:19.410
vos ken zayn mayn MESER far, far undz? natirlekh, az me zol zikh zen

00:25:20.529 --> 00:25:25.923
oykh tsu gebn der medine, un nit nor tsu trakhtn tsu nemen fun der medine.

00:25:28.359 --> 00:25:31.149
me zol visn der yunger dor

00:25:31.149 --> 00:25:31.898
az

00:25:32.088 --> 00:25:35.339
di medine iz dos vos halt undz oyfet

00:25:35.430 --> 00:25:40.031
vos kholile, kholile nit, vet keyner oyf undz nisht rakhmones hobn.

00:25:40.104 --> 00:25:41.350
keyne zakhn nit.

00:25:41.350 --> 00:25:42.596
zey zoln hitn

00:25:47.445 --> 00:25:49.161
un tayer haltn di medine.

00:25:49.655 --> 00:25:51.371
nokh eyn frage.

00:25:49.807 --> 00:25:50.729
o.

00:25:51.663 --> 00:25:58.290
ven hot ay- hot hot aykh gelungen zikh tsu trefn mit ayer mame, mit ayer shvester?

00:25:58.464 --> 00:26:00.655
mayn shvester un

00:26:00.692 --> 00:26:02.661
mayn muter

00:26:02.835 --> 00:26:06.370
hobn zikh di letste tsvey yor, dos heyst in dray un ferts- in

00:26:06.370 --> 00:26:12.060
tsvey un fertsiktn yor, biz tsvey un fertsiktn, zey zaynen gelofn fun mayn shtetl Korsovke

00:26:12.538 --> 00:26:14.003
ariber dem grenets

00:26:14.003 --> 00:26:17.139
un dortn zey ayngeladn in eshelones.

00:26:16.250 --> 00:26:17.899
in eyn un fertsikstn meynt ir.

00:26:17.212 --> 00:26:19.046
eyn un fertsiktn, antshuldikt.

00:26:19.524 --> 00:26:23.180
un ale dray shoyn derforn nokh, der foter un der muter un Rive,

00:26:23.355 --> 00:26:26.280
un me hot zey gefirt in eshelones.

00:26:26.280 --> 00:26:30.693
one broyt un one tsuker, one, vaser, one gornisht.

00:26:30.693 --> 00:26:34.169
oyf di v- oyf di stantsyes flegn zey arunter a bisl

00:26:34.169 --> 00:26:36.692
un farzukhn vos tsu farkoyfn un krign epes vos.

00:26:36.737 --> 00:26:39.510
merere khadoshim, biz m'hot zey derfirt

00:26:39.521 --> 00:26:40.545
biz

00:26:48.650 --> 00:26:49.741
eyn minut.

00:26:50.895 --> 00:26:52.841
oy-vey, kh'hob gekrogn

00:26:52.841 --> 00:26:56.424
genumen an ander tsetl. &lt;VELO KI, VELO KAYANA&gt;.

00:26:56.717 --> 00:27:01.406
dort hot men zey aruntergefirt, un dortn iz mayn foter &lt;vi ikh hob dertseylt frier&gt; gevorn krank in tifus,

00:27:01.442 --> 00:27:03.546
un dortn iz er geshtorbn. biz dan

00:27:03.635 --> 00:27:06.045
hobn zey gehungert kimat di gantse tsayt.

00:27:06.045 --> 00:27:08.911
zey hobn zikh dervust az nit vayt fun dortn

00:27:09.356 --> 00:27:11.218
iz do a spirt-fabrik

00:27:11.229 --> 00:27:13.316
vos dortn fodert zikh arbet.

00:27:14.790 --> 00:27:18.379
az zey hobn zikh derklibn mayn muter un mayn shvester Rive ahin,

00:27:18.587 --> 00:27:22.614
zey hobn zikh derf- der, der direktor fun der spirt-fabrik

00:27:22.687 --> 00:27:24.268
hot zey gevelt zen.

00:27:24.813 --> 00:27:26.658
mayn muter iz geven zeyer

00:27:26.658 --> 00:27:28.436
a gebildete froy

00:27:28.695 --> 00:27:31.443
un mayn shves- un mayn shvester avade un avade.

00:27:31.445 --> 00:27:33.549
vayl zi iz shoyn gegangen in universitet in Rige,

00:27:33.740 --> 00:27:38.173
un er hot di shvester arayngenumen als bukhhalt&lt;erin&gt;

00:27:38.347 --> 00:27:40.142
un di muter

00:27:40.142 --> 00:27:41.160
hot

00:27:41.233 --> 00:27:42.454
gezesn bayn

00:27:42.454 --> 00:27:44.048
gevikht di, di

00:27:44.048 --> 00:27:47.049
KHAKLAIM flegn kumen mit di tsuker-ribn,

00:27:47.291 --> 00:27:48.942
mit di tsuker-burikes,

00:27:48.942 --> 00:27:53.093
flegt men zey darfn vegn un vifl onshraybn un &lt;alts&gt;. dortn hobn zey gehat gut

00:27:53.093 --> 00:27:55.228
un fun dortn zaynen zey in

00:27:55.273 --> 00:27:56.480
eyn

00:27:56.488 --> 00:27:57.230
in

00:27:57.230 --> 00:28:02.591
finf un fertsiktn yor, az der krig hot zikh geendikt iz hobn zey zikh tsurikgekert keyn Rige.

00:28:03.170 --> 00:28:06.230
un dan hob ikh shoyn vayter frier dertseylt. dernokh hob ikh dervust

00:28:06.230 --> 00:28:08.600
a telegram vos ikh hob gekrogn fun zey.
